name: Tidesage
description:
"Tidesage"

This the first of many collaborations between Tolan and Pryces. After working together for years, the two have decided to make HEN their new home :)

This track tells the story of a young waterbender who leaves his unsupportive village in pursuit of his own potential.

Recorded, mixed, and mastered by Tolan & Pryces. Created on Ableton and Pro Tools 12.
Photo taken on an unnamed mountain in Leadville, Colorado.
